{"word":"G4982 - σώζω - sṓzō - sode'-zo - Heal","slug":"G4982","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σώζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sṓzō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sode'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Heal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - so&#x0304;zo&#x0304;</b> - <i>sode'-zo</i><p/>From a primary word <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C9;&#x0342;&#x03C2;</b> <b>so&#x0304;s&#x0304;</b> (contraction for the obsolete <b>&#x03C3;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>saos</b>, &ldquo;safe&rdquo;); to <i>save</i>, that is, <i>deliver</i> or <i>protect</i> (literally or figuratively): - heal, preserve, save (self), do well, be (make) whole."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4990\">G4990</a>, <a href=\"#/G4991\">G4991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4992\">G4992</a>"}]}